file: crates/ctx-verify/src/lib.rs
behavior: Crate root for ctx-verify, a broker that runs cargo/clippy/script checks and emits one capped JSON verification report so checking a change has bounded, deterministic token cost.
edit_notes:
  - Layering mirrors ctx-access: cli (argv/io) sits over checks (pure orchestration) sits over runner (process boundary); keep new code in the matching layer.
  - Report schema is described as part of the same family as the spec's audit report; changes to model.rs should stay schema-compatible with that.
functions:
invariants:
